high_descs: Walk towards the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the pan on the countertop.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the pan in the sink basin and wash it, picking it back up.
Make a right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the pan on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Wash a pan, put it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, then go forward and turn left at the counter adjacent to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the counter.
Turn around, step forward, then turn left to go to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn right and go straight until you reach the fridge, then turn left.
Open the fridge, put the pan inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the front of the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the dirty cast iron pan on the counter.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Wash the cast iron pan in the sink under running water and take it out.
Turn right to go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the pan on the top shelf in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Wash the pan and put it into the fridge.
